<color=Gold><b>Warmage -- Arcane Trickster</b></color>

This package for the warmage is built to give you the proper feats and skill ranks to qualify for the Arcane Trickster Prestige class.  You will still need to take levels in rogue to qualify for the prestige class.

This package does not give any special abilities to your character. It simply configures your skills and feats so that you don't have to.